    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy again. The engine currently has a noticeable knock and struggles to maintain idle, while the transmission exhibits slipping between gears. Externally, there is visible rust on the rocker panels and a few significant dents, and the interior shows heavy wear with several tears in the upholstery. This would be an ideal project car for someone with mechanical expertise or a source for parts.",
