    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptional vehicle, currently maintained in superlative condition. This unit represents a rare find for the discerning buyer, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original showroom luster. Meticulously serviced and preserved with exacting standards, this vehicle offers an uncompromising driving experience and mechanical integrity that is second to none. This is an invitation to acquire a premier example of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 48900.0,
