    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm so excited to show you this absolute gem. It\u2019s in truly stunning condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s been kept in such pristine shape that you'll have to see it to believe it. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically flawless and ready for your next adventure, this is the one. Come take a look!",
      "price": 44900.0,
