    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E46 M3, a definitive benchmark in longitudinal driving dynamics. This specimen features the S54 3.2L inline-six, boasting individual throttle bodies and a high-compression ratio that sings to an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory M-variable differential lock for optimal torque distribution. This vehicle is mechanically superlative: the dual-VANOS system has been precision-serviced, and the rear subframe\u2014a known point of fatigue\u2014has been proactively reinforced. The chassis remains incredibly rigid, supported by a refreshed suspension geometry and OEM bushings. Finished in original paint with no signs of oxidation or panel misalignment, this is a turn-key collector-grade machine for the discerning enthusiast who demands atmospheric purity and analog feedback.",
      "price": 48500.0,
